	<Language_en_US>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_PLAYER_GOOD_DESCRIPTION">
			<Text>Unlimited Power</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_PLAYER_GOOD_HELP">
			<Text>Our brightest minds have devised a technology by which we will be able to supply all of our energy needs! This is truely remarkable, heralding a new era for mankind.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_PLAYER_GOOD_HELP_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Desert Tiles yield +3 [ICON_GOLD] Gold and +3 [ICON_PRODUCTION].</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_PLAYER_GOOD_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_1">
			<Text>Solar panels are now able to self repair damage, increasing their lifespan outside of micromanaged plants a thousand fold! It will be the Desert that feeds the world's hunger for electricity!</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_PLAYER_GOOD_HELP_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Cities save {3_CityYieldGlobal}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_PLAYER_GOOD_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_2">
			<Text>Advances in nanostructuring allow us to finally perform the water splitting reaction and subsequent recombination in a single cell. Fuel is no longer necessary for everyday appliances.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_PLAYER_GOOD_HELP_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>Nuclear Plants switch to fusion power: +15% [ICON_PRODUCTION] Production and +15% [ICON_RESEARCH] Science.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_PLAYER_GOOD_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_3">
			<Text>No one ever thought it would come in time, but we finally have a fusion reactor that is self-sustaining and stable. The power of the sun in the palm of my hand.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_PLAYER_GOOD_HELP_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>All Cities produce {3_CityYieldGlobal}.</Text>
		</Row>
		<Row Tag="TXT_KEY_EVENT_AES_SCIENCE_PLAYER_GOOD_DESCRIPTION_CHOICE_4">
			<Text>By some miracle, the most destructive entity in the universe - antimatter - has not only been accessed, but also tamed. It will be some time before it can be used anywhere but the most secure facilities, but a single matter-drive can provide power to every City on the grid!</Text>
		</Row>
